OL,6,GBehind the scenes, the first visible
OL,7,Gadjustments to what's broadcast on
OL,8,GFreeview in preparation for regional
OL,9,GBBC One HD in England have taken place.
OL,11,FThe good news: this paves the way for
OL,12,Fthe end of the red slate on BBC One HD
OL,13,Fon Freeview, the last platform to
OL,14,Fbenefit from an upgrade.
OL,16,FThe bad news is that there are
OL,17,Fcurrently just five regional versions
OL,18,Fcovering all of England, reflecting the
OL,19,Fcurrent restricted availability of
OL,20,Fregional HD services in England. This
OL,21,Flimitation also affects ITV 1's HD
OL,22,Fviewers.
OL,3,CFirst preparations for BBC One HD
OL,4,CEnglish regions on Freeview
