PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1677266683
OL,6,FBoth BBC One HD and ITV 1 HD are
OL,7,Fcarried on Freeview multiplex PSB3, the
OL,8,Fonly multiplex set up to broadcast HD
OL,9,Fchannels.
OL,11,FEach Freeview channel has its own
OL,12,Fservice ID. Regional channels have a
OL,13,Fdifferent service ID for each version
OL,14,Fof their channel.
OL,16,FSince Monday, five new service IDs have
OL,17,Fcome into operation, pointing to the
OL,18,Fexisting BBC One HD videostream and
OL,19,Fsharing the same audio and data PIDs.
OL,3,CFirst preparations for BBC One HD
OL,4,CEnglish regions on Freeview
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/7
