OL,6,FAt the appointed time (not yet
OL,7,Fannounced), the England-wide BBC One HD
OL,8,Fvideostream will switch to a
OL,9,Fregionalised stream. The old national
OL,10,FBBC One HD service ID will cease and
OL,11,Fthe new regional service IDs will
OL,12,Fspring into action.
OL,14,FAs the video and audio PIDs aren't
OL,15,Fchanging, many receivers should
OL,16,Fseamlessly switch over, without
OL,17,Frequiring a retune.
OL,19,FAt present, the new service IDs are:
