OL,6,FTwo things need to happen: the
OL,7,Fmultiplex needs to be regionalised
OL,8,Ffurther or the BBC commences using some
OL,9,Fof the "creative solutions" it once
OL,10,Ftalked about regarding BBC One HD.
OL,12,FThis could be providing a red button
OL,13,Flink to the correct region on iPlayer
OL,14,For directly substituting the
OL,15,Fover-the-air broadcast channel with the
OL,16,Fcorrect region delivered online ` but
