PN,35006
SC,0006
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1677266683
OL,6,FBear in mind that the licence for the
OL,7,FFreeview HD multiplex (PSB3) expires in
OL,8,Fjust three years, with the BBC adopting
OL,9,Fa wait and see attitude on renewal.
OL,11,FIf the BBC does let the licence expire,
OL,12,Fthen it will need to either close down
OL,13,FHD channels again, or close SD channels
OL,14,Fon PSB1, allowing it to move HD
OL,15,Fchannels across there. Something made
OL,16,Feasier by the planned closure of CBBC
OL,17,Fand BBC Four.
OL,19,FAs PSB1 is set up as a fully
OL,20,Fregionalised multiplex, that would be
OL,21,Fgood news for HD users.
OL,3,CFirst preparations for BBC One HD
OL,4,CEnglish regions on Freeview
